{"lc": 1, "type": "constructor", "id": ["langchain", "schema", "document", "Document"], "kwargs": {"metadata": {"Header 1": "**5\ufe0f\u20e3 Why use theme.spacing.md**"}, "page_content": "Because your **screen padding uses md**.  \nFile: **Explore.tsx**  \npaddingHorizontal: theme.spacing.md  \nSo we match the same spacing:  \nmarginLeft: theme.spacing.md  \nIf you used a different value like:  \nmarginLeft: theme.spacing.sm  \nThen alignment breaks:  \n| edge | padding(md) | header  \n| edge | padding(sm) | Card1  \nEverything would look slightly shifted.  \nUsing **the same spacing token keeps the design system consistent**.", "type": "Document"}}